```r
allDf %>%
  dplyr::select(index,patientid,sampleloc,date) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  left_join(.,cn) -> cn

left_join(allDf,cn) %>%
  filter(index %in% sinspu) %>%
  dplyr::select(index,sampleloc,virus.bin,mean_cn) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = virus.bin,
             y = mean_cn,
             color = virus.bin)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  geom_jitter(width = 0.1,
              size = 5,
              alpha = 0.5) +
  scale_y_log10(name = \Mean 16S gene\ncopies per sample\") +
